 SHORT NOTES
css
. you style HTML elements using css by using th following tags
     1. id : styles specific element with id name.
     2. class :groups a styling and associates it with any element falling within the class.
     3. element names : styles any element without an id or a class.
. we have 3 forms of css
     1.internal : css is is written inside the html file
     2. external : css is written outside the html file
     3. inline : css is written using the style attribute inside the html file.

